{"tid":1864303,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PUBG向中國紅十字會捐款，千萬暖助武漢肺炎疫情","createTime":"2020-02-05T14:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T14:01:54.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9762d25e203de4870966a6c13164e6b6b993e94","tid":1864303,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"PUBG向中國紅十字會捐款，千萬暖助武漢肺炎疫情<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Panda/news/202001/200204-pubgg.jpg?versionId=dzzapi4CFBPGHCsi_XgPlTS9ekEemQmy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FPanda%2Fnews%2F202001%2F200204-pubgg.jpg%3FversionId%3Ddzzapi4CFBPGHCsi_XgPlTS9ekEemQmy&h=59e6e14b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV）疫情升溫，始發地中國確診數更是節節上升，作為遊戲開發商，PUBG 公司宣布捐贈人民幣 300 萬元，用於新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n疫情牽動人心，愛心不分國界，《絕地求生》開發商 PUBG 公司今（4）日在微博宣布向中國紅十字總會捐贈人民幣 300 萬元（折合新台幣約 1293 萬元），助力疫情防控工作。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n不過日前武漢紅十字會才爆出物資、善款分配等問題，許多中國玩家在底下留言表示這波捐款白給了，也有人跳出來緩頰，認為 PUBG 是捐給紅十字總會，應該不會有太多問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Panda/news/202001/200204-pubg-1.png?versionId=d0kLBf.nz0PDUlsjDl6OF5LZoo_Tbxem\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FPanda%2Fnews%2F202001%2F200204-pubg-1.png%3FversionId%3Dd0kLBf.nz0PDUlsjDl6OF5LZoo_Tbxem&h=f4e6617a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad503283e37644888bc522387a98dceeb2942028","tid":1864303,"uid":810,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"贈慶?<br />\n武漢玩緊真pubg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45593093d7ffc8ba38547f8e79bcac496ffa75ce","tid":1864303,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"不用PC也能玩絕地求生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}